      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WHISPERED (3) has a fair record and proved too strong last time to win by 0.8 lengths at this track in a handy 34.77 beating Paw Raelia. Well placed and will be tough to beat. LAMIA NONNA MIM (4) was out of the placings last time when sixth at The Meadows (30.83) but scored four back at this track (29.62). Form here at the trip sound including two wins. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. CHAMPLAIN (2) trailed the lead and fought on well to be beaten 6 lengths into second (34.98) at this track in a Free For All over 595m. Can measure up. MORAINE SARA (1) can return to form after missing the top-three at this circuit last time out.",
